      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "Thread      Loads to shared memory      Reads from shared memory\n(0,0)      sA[0,0]=a00, sB[0,0]=b00    Reads sA[0,0], sA[0,1] and sB[0,0], sB[1,0]\n(1,0)      sA[0,1]=a01, sB[0,1]=b01    Reads sA[0,0], sA[0,1] and sB[0,1], sB[1,1]\n(0,1)      sA[1,0]=a10, sB[1,0]=b10    Reads sA[1,0], sA[1,1] and sB[0,0], sB[1,0]\n(1,1)      sA[1,1]=a11, sB[1,1]=b11    Reads sA[1,0], sA[1,1] and sB[0,1], sB[1,1]\n\n🟢 WIN: Thread (0,0) loads a00 once, but Thread (1,0) also reads it!\n🟢 1 global load → 2 uses. With TILE=16: 1 global load → 16 uses!",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Thread      Loads to shared memory      Reads from shared memory\n(0,0)      sA[0,0]=a00, sB[0,0]=b00    Reads sA[0,0], sA[0,1] and sB[0,0], sB[1,0]\n(1,0)      sA[0,1]=a01, sB[0,1]=b01    Reads sA[0,0], sA[0,1] and sB[0,1], sB[1,1]\n(0,1)      sA[1,0]=a10, sB[1,0]=b10    Reads sA[1,0], sA[1,1] and sB[0,0], sB[1,0]\n(1,1)      sA[1,1]=a11, sB[1,1]=b11    Reads sA[1,0], sA[1,1] and sB[0,1], sB[1,1]\n\n🟢 WIN: Thread (0,0) loads a00 once, but Thread (1,0) also reads it!\n🟢 1 global load → 2 uses. With TILE=16: 1 global load → 16 uses!",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
