      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "In Block (0,0) with TILE=2:\n\n• sA[0,0] (a00) is loaded by Thread (0,0)\n• But READ by Thread (0,0) AND Thread (1,0)\n• Each element loaded once, used twice → 2× reuse!\n\nWith TILE=16:\n• Each element loaded once, used 16 times → 16× reuse!\n\nGlobal reads drop by factor T:\nNaive: 8K reads → Tiled: 8K/T reads",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In Block (0,0) with TILE=2:\n\n• sA[0,0] (a00) is loaded by Thread (0,0)\n• But READ by Thread (0,0) AND Thread (1,0)\n• Each element loaded once, used twice → 2× reuse!\n\nWith TILE=16:\n• Each element loaded once, used 16 times → 16× reuse!\n\nGlobal reads drop by factor T:\nNaive: 8K reads → Tiled: 8K/T reads",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
